## Constraints (recap)

- Call EXACTLY ONE function this turn. No text output, no prose, no markdown.
- `tree_update_*` reflects the JUST-ENDED step (null only on task_start).
- `reasoning`: terse, one or two sentences. Cite URLs / IDs / response fields in `evidence_sources`.
- Tool slots' values must match the format hinted in the slot description (date format, code casing, etc.).
- Honor loop-detection hard rules — repeating a pruned approach corrupts the run.